data.text:
The World According to John Coltrane

John Coltrane was the most innovative and influential jazz musician of the 1960s. The World According to John Coltrane, the only authorized documentary about him, shows that he was the pivotal musician of the mid-twentieth century. Coltrane was the first music master with a global perspective. The World According to John Coltrane captures a musical meeting between Art Ensemble of Chicago saxoph...
